-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.838ex; width:15.233ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle (g=
^{a}{\bmod {p}},g,p)}"></span>. To send her a message, Bob chooses a random=
 <i>b</i> and then sends Alice <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-ele=
ment-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" st=
yle=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" a=
lttext=3D"{\displaystyle g^{b}{\bmod {p}}}">
