            <mi>p</mi>
          </mrow>
        </mrow>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding=3D"application/x-tex">{\displaystyle g^{b}{\bmod {=
p}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
er/svg/4c284ce868345e5c39c15e477c89f0b0e1316a3c" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.671ex; width:8.906ex; height:3.009ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle g^{=
b}{\bmod {p}}}"></span> (unencrypted) together with the message encrypted w=
ith symmetric key <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline">=
<span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"displa=
y: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\d=
isplaystyle (g^{a})^{b}{\bmod {p}}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle=3D"true" scriptlevel=3D"0">
